rmal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我覺得女仔遇到岩既人要主動啲追<br />\n最後送上一條我幾鐘意既片俾大家參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CZqeKIE4VZU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCZqeKIE4VZU&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9jUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=a48a2457\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CZqeKIE4VZU</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"原來係咁樣<br />\n何必強求一個唔中意你嘅人呢<br />\n一旦開始委屈自己去討好其他人<br />\n就會一路扮落去，好辛苦架<br />\n咁不如做返你自己啦，自然會有欣賞你本來面目嘅人出現<br />\n<br />\n同埋我睇過呢條片喎<br />\n巴絲都係，中意就溝啦<br />\n最重要係自己開心姐"},{"pid":"6a3fb47bfca62e52afa282005f60ef3f345cdb05","tid":1662344,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36adbd4859e02734e5502c0838000f50fe8136c6","tid":1662344,"uid":243455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f563ce1a74c3442771f687755d36c29e1ef3e057","tid":1662344,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1488c7e937dad64560c21d7b7d2f861a78d4248","tid":1662344,"uid":243455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:22:01.000Z","msg":"摸邊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"摸髀 pat pat 波 腰 果d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"竟然有得摸波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n摸完扯之後咁點算？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"扯左咪扯左，可以點..."},{"pid":"de80d9bec196366acc67bcf97030af676ba265e9","tid":1662344,"uid":335179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fadbb689020a8e77aa6070c6adb1a05de65b95d","tid":1662344,"uid":243455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"168cb9020c74c4246efb54ac7021f597eeceacce","tid":1662344,"uid":335179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96e8a58e4927d3f7edd3321d4e85344e094e460a","tid":1662344,"uid":243455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:24:40.000Z",