000Z","msg":"我就係講緊呢個速食文化<br />\n好難令到你既本質會吸引到人<br />\n因為咁樣需要比較長既時間<br />\n相反某啲人用一啲所謂既Skill<br />\n就可以最快draw到人既注意<br />\n最後可以迷迷糊糊一齊左之後<br />\n先再諗可唔可以一齊行落去"},{"pid":"b30c2242f48b6554134f2f47f29ad1452678d9e8","tid":1662344,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43fea520bb071304e434e27a8679f77ebf661637","tid":1662344,"uid":289546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>扯左咪扯左，可以點...</blockquote>加＄進一步?</blockquote>尋日果位 講 其他人加幾千蚊叫佢上房 佢話唔做<br />\n唔知真當假啦<br />\n當然相信好多女都會做更一步既交易</blockquote>如果想要co<span style=\"color: red;\">n</span>tact 得唔得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠 打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"一直無提到，佢大陸妹黎，不過同佢溝通講廣東話，佢返左大陸讀書，我問下次約要幾時，答我下個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff22b65442bef043e78d34c55519a082fe472695","tid":1662344,"uid":289546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30c2242f48b6554134f2f47f29ad1452678d9e8","tid":1662344,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43fea520bb071304e434e27a8679f77ebf661637","tid":1662344,"uid":289546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>扯左咪扯左，可以點...</blockquote>加＄進一步?</blockquote>尋日果位 講 其他人加幾千蚊叫佢上房 佢話唔做<br />\n唔知真當假啦<br />\n當然相信好多女都會做更一步既交易</blockquote>如果想要co<span style=\"color: red;\">n</span>tact 得唔得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠 打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"一直無提到，佢大陸妹黎，不過同佢溝通講廣東話，佢返左大陸讀書，我問下次約要幾時，答我下個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"最近想搵人陪下<img src=\